    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this car to believe it\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, and it drives just as smooth as it looks. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously kept, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love! \u2728",
