    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a quintessential 'time capsule' specimen, preserved in a state that rivals its original delivery day. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like metallic finish that has been professionally ceramic coated; there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin is immaculate and smoke-free, featuring premium leather upholstery with zero bolster wear and carpets that have been protected by factory mats since day one. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced by brand specialists with a comprehensive binder of maintenance records included. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, ensuring all rubber seals and plastic components remain supple and fresh. Every electronic feature and mechanical system operates with precision. This sale includes both original master keys, all factory manuals, and the original window sticker. Truly a museum-quality example for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
